:"a13ac01206649680e0605d64975a9d7c289b9af9","tid":2197823,"uid":60924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:05:24.000Z","msg":"咁同台灣做生意得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848d7d3186a1cc49f634b00951fb9139590d61b3","tid":2197823,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"人地去台灣 但禁入強國<br />\n點解唔係禁入台灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae802909adeee3902f02caf4cbe1cfd3af369c16","tid":2197823,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"中國太強硬、太自以為是"},{"pid":"2f6daf5ea6d564cdb798c1aff01c1b97c0ac066c","tid":2197823,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"848d7d3186a1cc49f634b00951fb9139590d61b3","tid":2197823,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"人地去台灣 但禁入強國<br />\n點解唔係禁入台灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"間接承認兩國"},{"pid":"192234c88431bd833511108061e16d59c550c67e","tid":2197823,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"死垃圾<br />\n打未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印度佬都夠薑過支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15c582c94c305bc9af0e2af66ade4520af4fd2b","tid":2197823,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"去中國游水咩屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95852c15522d2efb58000975c56f8e0d609a0aa","tid":2197823,"uid":315761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"毒撚: 禁止女神溝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ee0b297424c8c44d83ca22cbe8488d68c9d426","tid":2197823,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"咁以後剩去得台灣"},{"pid":"a2a6c28ff9bab172c7d4ae607d3ca40331802f6d","tid":2197823,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中共促捷克主流人士與維特齊劃清界線</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/09/11 09:58<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北11日電）據發布，中共中央對外聯絡部部長宋濤近日與捷克共產黨主席、眾議院第一副議長菲利普視訊通話時表示，希望捷克主流人士與率團訪台的捷克參議院議長維特齊等人「劃清界線」。<br />\n<br />\n據中共中聯部官網發布，宋濤9日與菲利普（Vojtech Filip）視訊通話時表示，中捷建立戰略夥伴關係是雙方著眼未來作出的戰略選擇，符合兩國和兩國人民的根本利益。令人遺憾的是，近期維特齊（Milos Vystrcil）一意孤行赴台進行所謂「訪問」，粗暴干涉中國內政，嚴重破壞了中捷關係政治基礎，中方對此強烈譴責和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n宋濤重申中國在「台灣問題」上的原則立場，表示中方歷來主張國家不分大小一律平等，但平等應該是雙向的，尊重也必須是相互的。中方歡迎捷克總統等政要近日就該事件作出積極表態，希望捷克主流人士與維特齊之流「劃清界限」，堅持「一個中國」原則，以實際行動維護好中捷關係發展大局。<br />\n<br />\n發布稱，菲利普表示，維特齊一行訪台是捷克極少數人的個人行為，不會改變捷克對中政策，也不代表捷克民眾的意願。絕大多數捷克民眾都積極支持同中國加強友好與合作。<br />\n<br />\n他說，捷共堅定支持「一個中國」原則，支持中國企業積極參與捷各領域建設，期待為增進捷中兩國互信貢獻力量，並共同維護公正合理的國際秩序。（編輯：楊昇儒）1090911<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009110030.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009110030.aspx&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=ef572f6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009110030.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"7213d1da6b71d83fe06d356e2f5d86a4e5bd3f26","tid":2197823,"uid":70227,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"不准入境中國<br />\n可以入境台灣<br />\n自己承認台灣唔係中國一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081ff8d3d843929e3de02d77fa7dd7d19be2cb35","tid":21