路前食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940c145aad32ce0375403bfce0ade348e4371d83","tid":2197823,"uid":180251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"強國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86d342f208ba165536e40c4fd28af2b8e0b3019","tid":2197823,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"捷克業界人士說，中方報復在預料中，但如此幼稚與規定得這麼清楚，令人驚訝。"},{"pid":"66aec3e36d537c8fe5fc1e427db17364b400eca5","tid":2197823,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚驚呀.gif"},{"pid":"254d76314ed58dbd4445eb467d2607d0cb41636e","tid":2197823,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2a6c28ff9bab172c7d4ae607d3ca40331802f6d","tid":2197823,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中共促捷克主流人士與維特齊劃清界線</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/09/11 09:58<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北11日電）據發布，中共中央對外聯絡部部長宋濤近日與捷克共產黨主席、眾議院第一副議長菲利普視訊通話時表示，希望捷克主流人士與率團訪台的捷克參議院議長維特齊等人「劃清界線」。<br />\n<br />\n據中共中聯部官網發布，宋濤9日與菲利普（Vojtech Filip）視訊通話時表示，中捷建立戰略夥伴關係是雙方著眼未來作出的戰略選擇，符合兩國和兩國人民的根本利益。令人遺憾的是，近期維特齊（Milos Vystrcil）一意孤行赴台進行所謂「訪問」，粗暴干涉中國內政，嚴重破壞了中捷關係政治基礎，中方對此強烈譴責和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n宋濤重申中國在「台灣問題」上的原則立場，表示中方歷來主張國家不分大小一律平等，但平等應該是雙向的，尊重也必須是相互的。中方歡迎捷克總統等政要近日就該事件作出積極表態，希望捷克主流人士與維特齊之流「劃清界限」，堅持「一個中國」原則，以實際行動維護好中捷關係發展大局。<br />\n<br />\n發布稱，菲利普表示，維特齊一行訪台是捷克極少數人的個人行為，不會改變捷克對中政策，也不代表捷克民眾的意願。絕大多數捷克民眾都積極支持同中國加強友好與合作。<br />\n<br />\n他說，捷共堅定支持「一個中國」原則，支持中國企業積極參與捷各領域建設，期待為增進捷中兩國互信貢獻力量，並共同維護公正合理的國際秩序。（編輯：楊昇儒）1090911<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009110030.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009110030.aspx&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=ef572f6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009110030.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"永遠最叻就係煽動內部分裂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6435a3eb07bd30ef73a3781bb344e28c0b7293","tid":2197823,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ad4db0a72d431fdc056c3641e8656df1175997","tid":2197823,"uid":128213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60febe70495ad39f148277cf73016527131feae1","tid":2197823,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"可惜既係成個歐洲只得捷克夠膽訪台，其他崇尚自由民主國家繼續睇唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"No la.<br />\n捷克呢單野唔多唔少代表緊歐洲第一步接觸"},{"pid":"82c630cb3b967af19bd2c00aa4d6b3544175e426","tid":2197823,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"#ok#lm noticed with thx"},{"pid":"ef8869395ecfe03a877868ec742b536b41817270","tid":2197823,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c630cb3b967af19bd2c00aa4d6b3544175e426","tid":2197823,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"#ok#lm noticed with thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfa844b96fd7c9961abe20f0ba157528cb949ab","tid":2197823,"uid":265521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"其實都真係好幼稚"},{"pid":"e61555b1080d06e76e46f13d70466ca8867f25d2","tid":2197823,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0